            "id": 452096,
            "title": "Mazzei Chianti Classico Riserva Ser Lapo",
            "description": "Ruby red with violet nuances, this wine has bright aromas of fresh cherries mingle with notes of thyme and subtle smoky nuances. In the mouth, this wine has a bright acid structure providing a lively quality. Cranberry, raspberry and red cherry dominate with hints of leather, cedar and cocoa powder. Some earthiness in the finish and ripe soft tannins.Pasta with meat sauces, stews, grilled meats and mid-aged cheeses.",
