        "pairingText": "Asian on the menu? Try pairing with Riesling, Gewurztraminer, and Chenin Blanc. The best wine for Asian food depends on the cuisine and dish - of course - but these acidic whites pair with a number of traditional meals, spicy or not. One wine you could try is Engel Wines Riesling - Kosher. It has 5 out of 5 stars and a bottle costs about 20 dollars.",
